title: Hex-Rays IDA Pro v6.6 Incl Decompiler SDK Utils And Patch Repack
description:
Hex-Rays IDA 6.6.141224 with x86 and ARM Decompiler v2.0.0.140605

1.) Install IDA 6.6.140604 using the installer and password in Setup/IDA_PRO_SETUP
2.) Upgrade to IDA 6.6.141224 by replacing install files with the ones in Patch/Patch
3.) Enjoy!

Notes:
You can open old databases by installing the plugin in Patch/IDA DB Fix
The full SDK for IDA development is in SDK
Optional python plugins are located in Plugins/IDAPython-1.7.0_IDA6.6_py2.7_win32
Optional BinDiff and WinDbg are also included in Setup
